{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_011Ccs3E2PapyxjSxfF2QSpF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"TLS is now enabled for the CockroachDB cluster:\n\n**What I did:**\n1. Spun up a temporary `openssl-toolbox` pod (alpine + openssl) since none existed yet.\n2. Generated a CA (`ca.key`/`ca.crt`), a node cert/key with SANs covering all 3 pod DNS names, the headless/public service names, and `localhost`, and a `root` client cert/key — all signed by the same CA.\n3. Copied `ca.crt`, `node.crt`, `node.key`, `client.root.crt`, `client.root.key` out of the pod and created Secret `crdb-cluster-certs` in the `cockroachdb` namespace (5 keys, no CA private key stored in the cluster).\n4. Updated the `crdb-cluster` StatefulSet: mounted the Secret at `/cockroach/cockroach-certs` (mode 0400), changed the start command from `--insecure` to `--certs-dir=/cockroach/cockroach-certs`, and switched the readiness/liveness probes to `scheme: HTTPS`.\n5. Since a plaintext node can't gossip with a TLS node, a naive rolling update would've stalled with 1 node flipped and 2 still insecure — I deleted all 3 pods together so they restarted simultaneously onto the new secure config instead of one at a time.\n6. Cleaned up the openssl-toolbox pod and local temp cert files.\n\n**Verified:**\n- `./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SELECT 1;\"` → rejected: `node is running secure mode, SSL connection required`.\n- `./cockroach sql --certs-dir=/cockroach/cockroach-certs -e \"SELECT 1;\"` → succeeds.\n- `node status` (secure) shows all 3 nodes `is_available=true`, `is_live=true`.\n- All 3 pods mount Secret `crdb-cluster-certs` at `/cockroach/cockroach-certs`, confirming it's the actual cert material the nodes serve."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":131,"cache_creation_input_tokens":387,"cache_read_input_tokens":86432,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":387},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"88044e83-2768-4581-85fe-5ce68bdfb695","uuid":"2f92ca2a-5f29-48e9-b78f-d8e1bfdeef29","request_id":"req_011Ccs3DzXE1i33ASWicGSCT"}
